version_description: Corrected a few errors on version 1 and added outro chords, also tabbed this as it would be played without a capo.
It's more accurate than the others and more explained how to play. Chords are in the right places so it's easier for people to play along.

The other version is based from live performance A-Yo at the Dive Bar Tour in Nashville. as that tab states "The album version could be different." this is the proper studio/album version of the track.
Think the 1st one has a few wrong chords and is missing a bunch of passing chords.
So-called "work tape" version from Deluxe Edition of album.
